sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Code
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant SS as AI4RAGSearchSpace
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker
    participant Embed as Embedding Model<br/>(LS / OpenAI)
    participant VS as Vector Store<br/>(LS / Chroma)
    participant Retriever as Retriever
    participant FM as Foundation Model<br/>(LS / OpenAI)
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    participant Handler as EventHandler<br/>(Local / KFP)

    Note over User,Handler: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    User->>Exp: search(benchmark_data, search_space)
    activate Exp

    Note over Exp,MPS: Phase 1: Model Pre-Selection
    Exp->>MPS: select_models(data_sample)
    activate MPS
    MPS->>Chunker: chunk(documents)
    Chunker-->>MPS: chunks[]
    MPS->>Embed: embed(chunks)
    Embed->>LS: POST /embeddings<br/>HTTPS, API Key
    LS-->>Embed: vectors[]
    Embed-->>MPS: embeddings
    MPS->>VS: insert(embeddings)
    Note over VS: ChromaDB in-memory<br/>(for pre-selection)
    MPS->>Retriever: query(questions)
    Retriever->>VS: similarity_search()
    VS-->>Retriever: contexts[]
    MPS->>FM: generate(context + question)
    FM->>LS: POST /chat/completions<br/>HTTPS, API Key
    LS-->>FM: answer
    FM-->>MPS: response
    MPS->>Eval: evaluate(predictions, ground_truth)
    Eval-->>MPS: scores{faithfulness, correctness}
    MPS-->>Exp: filtered_models[]
    deactivate MPS

    Note over Exp,GAM: Phase 2: HPO Iterations
    Exp->>SS: prepare_search_space(filtered_models)
    SS->>LS: GET /models/list<br/>HTTPS, API Key
    LS-->>SS: available_models[]
    SS-->>Exp: valid_combinations[]

    loop For each HPO iteration
        Exp->>GAM: suggest_next(observations)
        GAM-->>Exp: next_params

        Note over Exp,FM: Phase 3: RAG Pattern Evaluation
        Exp->>Chunker: chunk(documents, params)
        Chunker-->>Exp: chunks[]
        Exp->>Embed: embed(chunks)
        Embed->>LS: POST /embeddings<br/>HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>Embed: vectors[]
        Embed-->>Exp: embeddings
        Exp->>VS: create_store + insert
        VS->>LS: POST /vector_stores/create<br/>HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>VS: store_id
        VS->>LS: POST /vector_io/insert<br/>HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>VS: ok

        par Parallel query execution (ThreadPool, max=10)
            Exp->>Retriever: query(question)
            Retriever->>VS: similarity_search()
            VS->>LS: POST /vector_io/query<br/>HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>VS: results[]
            VS-->>Retriever: contexts[]
            Retriever-->>Exp: context
            Exp->>FM: generate(context + question)
            FM->>LS: POST /chat/completions<br/>HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>FM: answer
            FM-->>Exp: response
        end

        Exp->>Eval: evaluate(all_predictions, ground_truth)
        Eval-->>Exp: scores + confidence_intervals

        Exp->>GAM: update(params, score)
        Exp->>Handler: on_pattern_evaluated(payload)
    end

    Exp->>Handler: on_experiment_completed(results)
    Handler-->>User: results (JSON files / KFP outputs)
    deactivate Exp
